You are helping me build a personal portfolio website.

Stack: Next.js 14 (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion

Rules:
- Always use the App Router (not Pages Router)
- Use TypeScript for every file
- Use Tailwind for all styling, no inline styles
- Keep components small and reusable
- Use 'use client' only when necessary
- Follow accessibility best practices
- Ask before installing new packages